me=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'At this moment, the two were training with Beerus.',30640,7,26640,'Lúc này, cả hai đang luyện tập cùng Beerus.'),(80,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.608131','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.608131','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'He handed their training over to Weiss, and as long as they practiced too',34880,7,30640,'Ông giao việc huấn luyện của họ cho Weiss, và chỉ cần họ tập luyện quá'),(81,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.611307','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.611307','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'loudly and made noise while he was resting, he would become furious.',39520,7,34880,'ồn ào trong lúc ông nghỉ ngơi, ông sẽ nổi giận.'),(82,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.613857','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.613857','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'His first reaction was shock.',42080,7,39520,'Phản ứng đầu tiên của anh là sự kinh ngạc.'),(83,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.615788','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.615788','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'It was the first time Wang Ting had seen Weiss show such an expression, because he',46280,7,42080,'Đây là lần đầu tiên Wang Ting thấy Weiss lộ ra biểu cảm như vậy, bởi vì trước đó ông'),(84,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.615788','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.615788','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'had always worn a relaxed smile before.',50120,7,46280,'luôn giữ một nụ cười thoải mái.'),(85,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.620367','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.620367','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'Wang Ting sat down next to Weiss.',52800,7,50120,'Wang Ting ngồi xuống bên cạnh Weiss.'),(86,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.623439','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.623439','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'Weiss continued to ask.',55519,7,52800,'Weiss tiếp tục hỏi.'),(87,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.625961','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.625961','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'It seems that Lord Wang Ting has gained something from this retreat, and his temperament',59520,7,55520,'Có vẻ như ngài Wang Ting đã thu được điều gì đó từ lần bế quan này, và khí chất của ông'),(88,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.629912','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.629912','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'and the power he exudes are very different from before.',63600,7,59520,'cũng như sức mạnh toát ra đã rất khác trước.'),(89,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.629912','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.629912','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'After fighting for a while, Wang Ting said, \"Maybe I broke through to a new realm.\"',67640,7,63600,'Sau khi chiến đấu một lúc, Wang Ting nói: \"Có lẽ tôi đã đột phá sang một cảnh giới mới.\"'),(90,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.633695','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.633695','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'What does that mean?',68640,7,67640,'Điều đó có nghĩa là gì?'),(91,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.633695','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.633695','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'Meaning, also known as artistic conception, is something ethereal.',73400,7,68640,'Ý cảnh, còn được gọi là cảnh giới nghệ thuật, là một thứ rất trừu tượng.'),(92,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.633695','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.633695','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'Weiss explained slowly.',76240,7,73400,'Weiss chậm rãi giải thích.'),(93,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.644549','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.644549','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'And the main condition for generating this state is that one\'s combat effectiveness',80240,7,76240,'Và điều kiện chính để đạt được trạng thái này là thực lực chiến đấu'),(94,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.650112','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.650112','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'breaks through the level of a God of Destruction. At present, Master Beerus has',84840,7,80240,'phải vượt qua cấp độ của Thần Hủy Diệt. Hiện tại, ngài Beerus vẫn chưa'),(95,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.653497','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.653497','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'not comprehended this state. As far as I know, the only one who has',89960,7,84840,'lĩnh hội được trạng thái này. Theo tôi biết, người duy nhất đã'),(96,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.654254','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.654254','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'comprehended it is the God of Destruction of Universe Two, Lord Helles.',95080,7,89960,'lĩnh hội được nó là Thần Hủy Diệt của Vũ trụ thứ Hai, ngài Helles.'),(97,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.659228','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.659228','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'He is also the one whom Lord Beerus has always wanted to surpass.',101360,7,95080,'Ông cũng là người mà Beerus luôn muốn vượt qua.'),(98,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.665625','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.665625','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'What kind of ability does your state have?',103440,7,101360,'Trạng thái của bạn có năng lực như thế nào?'),(99,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.666579','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.666579','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'That depends on you to figure out.',105520,7,103440,'Điều đó phụ thuộc vào chính bạn tìm ra.'),(100,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.666579','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.666579','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'After one gains this state, it can be used in battle. That is the true',109760,7,105520,'Sau khi đạt được trạng thái này, có thể sử dụng nó trong chiến đấu. Đó mới là'),(101,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.666579','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.666579','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'power of a God of Destruction.',111920,7,109760,'sức mạnh thực sự của một Thần Hủy Diệt.'),(102,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.681443','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.681443','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'If Master Beerus were not so lazy, with his talent, he would have every chance to comprehend',116800,7,111920,'Nếu Beerus không quá lười biếng, với thiên phú của mình, ông hoàn toàn có cơ hội lĩnh hội'),(103,'2026-04-14 13:33:14.683455','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)','2026-04-14 13:33:14.683455','User(email=admin 20024, password=null, fullName=null, avatar=null, location=null, learningLevel=null, role=2)',0,'Perfected Ultra Instinct and grasp the power of will, becoming truly powerful.',121760,7,116800,'Bản năng vô cực hoàn hảo và nắm bắt sức mạnh ý chí, trở nên thực sự mạnh mẽ.');
